'''''Sanctus Ignis''''' is the [[debut album]] by French [[progressive metal|progressive]]/[[neo-classical metal]] band [[Adagio (band)|Adagio]], released on May 8, 2001 in [[France]] by Nothing To Say, and in [[Europe]] by [[Limb Music]].

